                            "is_deleted": false,
                            "key_observations": "_External Auditors are Completing all the allocated audits for the First Round - However, due to vendors not uploading proper documents , Second round of audits not able to finish for all the invoies. Eventually both Karma and External auditors receiving less monthly payment. ( Ex. We have allocated 450 audits Mainak , He is able to Complete all the audits for the 1st Round, and He rejected audits due to vendors not uploading authenticated documents, By which he will not able to complete Final rond of audit. Due to this Process final closed audits will be aprox 100 only and payment also eligible for only closed audit as per JLL Terms. this issue has been raised with JLL and Action plan is still pending.",
